### ============================================
### MazadPay API - User Authentication Flow
### ============================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082/v1/api
@adminToken = {{$dotenv ADMIN_TOKEN}}
@devOtpCode = {{$dotenv DEV_OTP_CODE}}
@userPhone = 33333333
@userPin = 1234
@userFullName = Ahmed Harrouni
@userEmail = ahmed@example.com
@userCity = Tunis

### ============================================
### 🔐 AUTHENTICATION FLOW (Required order!)
### ============================================

### 1️⃣ REGISTER - Create a new unverified user
### Required fields: phone, pin, full_name, email
### Optional fields: city
### Response: { success: true, message: "Registration successful. OTP will be sent." }
# @name registerUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{userPhone}}",
    "pin": "{{userPin}}",
    "full_name": "{{userFullName}}",
    "email": "{{userEmail}}",
    "city": "{{userCity}}"
}

### 2️⃣ SEND OTP - Request OTP code for verification
### Response: { success: true, message: "OTP sent successfully" }
### ⚠️ In DEV mode, OTP code is in .env: DEV_OTP_CODE
# @name sendOTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{userPhone}}",
    "purpose": "register"
}

### 3️⃣ VERIFY OTP - Verify OTP code (marks user as verified)
### Use code from DEV_OTP_CODE in .env or "123456" in development
### Response: { success: true, message: "OTP verified successfully" }
# @name verifyOTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{userPhone}}",
    "code": "{{devOtpCode}}",
    "purpose": "register"
}

### 4️⃣ LOGIN - Now login works! ✅
### Response: { success: true, data: { token: "jwt_token", user: {...} } }
# @name loginUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{userPhone}}",
    "pin": "{{userPin}}"
}

### ============================================
### 👤 USER ENDPOINTS (Requires Token from Login)
### ============================================

### 5️⃣ GET ME - Get current user info
### Requires: Authorization Bearer token from login
# @name getMe
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser.response.body.data.token}}

### 6️⃣ GET NOTIFICATIONS - User notifications
# @name getNotifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser.response.body.data.token}}

### 7️⃣ GET FAVORITES - User favorite auctions
# @name getFavorites
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser.response.body.data.token}}

### ============================================
### 🔐 ADMIN SECTION
### ============================================

### 8️⃣ GENERATE ADMIN INVITATION (Admin only)
### Requires: ADMIN_TOKEN from .env
# @name generateInvitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/invitations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{}

### 9️⃣ REGISTER NEW ADMIN using invitation token
### Use token from generateInvitation response
# @name registerAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{generateInvitation.response.body.data.token}}",
    "phone": "99999999",
    "full_name": "New Admin User",
    "email": "newadmin@mazadpay.com",
    "pin": "1234"
}
